{"tid":796853,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★[又贏]社署周四向領綜援學生發放$2000津貼  毋須另行申請","createTime":"2018-08-28T05:08:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-28T15:16:07.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d4b323d7baf76ab4d19941094d9012b180ae3e1c","tid":796853,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T05:08:40.000Z","msg":"2018-08-28 HKT 12:39<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n社署後日開始向領取綜援學生發放一次性津貼。<br />\n<br />\n社署表示，有關安排是預算案公布的措施之一。在2018/19學年符合資格領取綜援計劃與選定項目定額津貼的學生，每人可一次過<span style=\"color: red;\">獲發2千元津貼</span>。<br />\n<br />\n有關款項以現行發放綜援的方式支付，領款人毋須另行申請。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1414918-20180828.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1414918-20180828.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=CMkZ1i9izpj5%2FSJUmlXWNSwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=ef59d8c2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1414918-20180828.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=1625ac5f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1414918-20180828.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"8c7d2de221173d02ce2e6ebe3811aeac5439f76f","tid":796853,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T05:10:03.000Z","msg":"最大贏家.jpg<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0418e79fbe8e607bdb0dcf7963af4b1390d7902","tid":796853,"uid":26752,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T05:10:15.000Z","msg":"老綜皇道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3327793c326dca82a75bea898f81fd5942aed38","tid":796853,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T05:10:57.000Z","msg":"補貼買ps4 pro<img src=\"